== 發行 ==

2015年6月30日，派拉蒙宣布，電影正式標題為《13 Hours: The Secret Soldiers of Benghazi》，並定於2016年1月15日的[[馬丁·路德·金紀念日|馬丁·路德·金紀念日]]釋出<ref>{{cite news|last1=A. Lincoln|first1=Ross|title=Paramount’s ’13 Hours’ Benghazi Drama Confirmed For MLK Weekend 2016|url=http://deadline.com/2015/06/benghazi-drama-13-hours-benghazi-drama-in-theaters-mlk-2016-1201464746/|accessdate=2015-07-02|work=deadline.com|date=2015-06-30|archive-date=2017-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170703134246/http://deadline.com/2015/06/benghazi-drama-13-hours-benghazi-drama-in-theaters-mlk-2016-1201464746/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2016年1月12日，影片在[[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]][[阿灵顿|阿灵顿]][[AT&T体育场|AT&T体育场]]首映<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2016/01/06/movies/13-hours-gives-benghazi-attack-cinematic-treatment.html?ref=movies&referer=https://www.nytimes.com/pages/movies/index.html&nytmobile=0|title=‘13 Hours’ Gives Benghazi Attack Cinematic Treatment|first=Michael|last=Cieplyjan|work=The New York Times|date=2016-01-06|accessdate=2016-01-06|archive-date=2019-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190112002705/https://www.nytimes.com/2016/01/06/movies/13-hours-gives-benghazi-attack-cinematic-treatment.html?ref=movies&referer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2Fpages%2Fmovies%2Findex.html&nytmobile=0|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 評價 ===

《13小時：班加西的秘密士兵》獲得了褒貶不一的評價。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]根據195篇專業影評持有50%的評級，平均得分5.5／10；該網站共識：「《13小時：班加西的秘密士兵》對[[麥可·貝|麥可·貝]]來說是成熟內斂的努力，儘管它的故事沒有完全擁有根據事實的效用」<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/13_hours_the_secret_soldiers_of_benghazi/ |title=13 Hours: The Secret Soldiers of Benghazi (2016) |website=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=2016-01-15 |archive-date=2016-01-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160118230409/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/13_hours_the_secret_soldiers_of_benghazi/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]得分48，[[IMDB|IMDB]]得7.3，評價兩極<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/13-hours-the-secret-soldiers-of-benghazi |title=13 Hours: The Secret Soldiers of Benghazi reviews |website=Metacritic |accessdate=2016-01-14 |archive-date=2016-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160116091614/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/13-hours-the-secret-soldiers-of-benghazi |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《[[西雅圖時報|西雅圖時報]]》的索倫·安德烈森從滿分四星中給了電影三星的評價，他批評電影缺乏鮮明的角色，但《13小時》整體來說是「引人入勝」<ref name="seattlereview">{{cite web|url=http://www.seattletimes.com/entertainment/movies/13-hours-a-gripping-look-at-what-happened-in-benghazi/?|title=13 Hours: a gripping look at what happened in Benghazi|author=Soren Andersen|publisher=Seattle Times|date=2016-01-14|accessdate=2016-01-14|archive-date=2016-01-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160130225203/http://www.seattletimes.com/entertainment/movies/13-hours-a-gripping-look-at-what-happened-in-benghazi/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

利比亚人民强烈谴责影片<ref>{{cite web|title=Hollywood Benghazi film sparks controversy inside Libya|url=http://nypost.com/2015/10/20/hollywood-benghazi-film-sparks-controversy-inside-libya/|website=New York Post|accessdate=2017-03-30|date=2015-10-20|archive-date=2017-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170330181606/http://nypost.com/2015/10/20/hollywood-benghazi-film-sparks-controversy-inside-libya/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。许多人认为他们拯救美国大使的贡献受到忽视<ref name="angry libyans">{{cite web|title=Angry Libyans slam Michael Bay's Benghazi attack thriller|url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/2015/oct/22/michael-bay-13-hours-the-secret-soldiers-of-benghazi-libyan-politicians-bloggers-criticism-social-media|website=The Guardians|accessdate=2017-03-30|date=2015-10-22|archive-date=2017-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170330180123/https://www.theguardian.com/film/2015/oct/22/michael-bay-13-hours-the-secret-soldiers-of-benghazi-libyan-politicians-bloggers-criticism-social-media|dead-url=no}}</ref>。利比亚外交部发言人萨拉赫·贝尔纳巴（{{lang|en|Salah Belnaba}}）批评影片对利比亚人民的描绘“狂热、无知”<ref name="sparking anger">{{cite web|title=Hollywood Benghazi film sparking anger inside Libya|url=http://www.cbsnews.com/news/hollywood-benghazi-film-sparking-anger-inside-libya/|website=CBS News|accessdate=2017-03-30|date=2015-10-20|archive-date=2017-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170331030257/http://www.cbsnews.com/news/hollywood-benghazi-film-sparking-anger-inside-libya/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。利比亚文化和信息部长奥马尔·加瓦里里（{{lang|en|Omar Gawaari}}）同样批评电影：“影片将没能拯救大使的美国探员当成英雄”，并补充道，“迈克尔·贝将美国保护动荡地区公民的失败转化成完全描绘美国英雄主义的典型动作片<ref name="angry libyans" /><ref name="sparking anger" />。”

